notes.text: This advisory aggregates security fixes for the mecab-ipadic SRPM in CIQ LTS for Rocky Linux 8.8. It addresses 87 CVEs: CVE-2022-4899, CVE-2023-21911, CVE-2023-21919, CVE-2023-21920, CVE-2023-21929, and 82 more.
